=Description=

"Participatory Studies is a burgeoning field of study that honors a metaphysical or speculative realism  while recognizing the radical pluralism of our planetary age.

In turning to the rich diversity and complexity of our lived experience, the “participatory turn” finds itself engaged in and as participatory events with a curiosity about our participatory predicament. These themes will be explored in a variety of ways throughout this website."
(http://participatorystudies.com/about/)


